# ğŸ“Š fireviz - A Simple & Fast Data Visualization Library  

**fireviz** is a lightweight Python package for quick and insightful data visualizations. It allows you to generate various plots using **Matplotlib, Seaborn, Plotly, and NetworkX** with minimal effort.  

## ğŸš€ Features  
âœ” Supports multiple plot types: `scatter`, `bar`, `line`, `heatmap`, `pie`, `treemap`, `network`, `sankey`, and more!  
âœ” Handles both **Pandas DataFrames and Series** automatically.  
âœ” Built-in **Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)** function.  
âœ” Uses **Seaborn & Plotly** for professional-quality visuals.  
âœ” Requires minimal configuration â€“ just pass your data!  

---

## ğŸ“¦ Installation  

```sh
pip install fireviz
```


