## ğŸ“Š Supported Plot Types  

| Plot Type    | `kind` Parameter |
|-------------|----------------|
| Scatter Plot | `"scatter"` |
| Line Chart | `"line"` |
| Box Plot | `"box"` |
| Bar Chart | `"bar"` |
| Bubble Chart | `"bubble"` |
| Area Chart | `"area"` |
| Heatmap | `"heatmap"` |
| Pie Chart | `"pie"` |
| Donut Chart | `"donut"` |
| Treemap | `"treemap"` |
| Funnel Chart | `"funnel"` |
| Waterfall Chart | `"waterfall"` |
| Choropleth Map | `"choropleth"` |
| Radar Chart | `"radar"` |
| Network Graph | `"network"` |
| Sankey Diagram | `"sankey"` |
| Gantt Chart | `"gantt"` |
| Bullet Chart | `"bullet"` |
| Density Plot | `"density"` |
| Stacked Bar Chart | `"stacked_bar"` |

